name: PrettyMuchYou'reAwesome
0: ”Alexa, tell me how awesome I am.”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: me how awesome i am
des: Have you ever doubted your awesomeness for even a millisecond? Worry no more! Just ask Alexa "tell me how awesome I am" and she'll report back with a plethora of amazing abilities you possess. Want to be reminded that "You know the last digit of pi." or that "You are the reason why Waldo is hiding."? Then put this skill to good use! You'll walk away being reminded of your awesomeness and how jealous all of your plentiful friends are of you. Awesome. Just Awesome.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
